 Popular Nigerian politician, Abike Kafayat Oluwatoyin Dabiri-Erewa has lost her mother. The former member of the Nigeria Federal House of Representatives took to Instagram today, February 3, 2021, to share the sad news. She wrote, “My super mum passed on peacefully at 90. Alhamdulilah. She laid Peacefully, gracefully as she smiled, waved and said “I want to sleep”
We give God the glory for a life well spent.” View this post on Instagram A post shared by Hon. Abike Dabiri-Erewa (@abikedabiri)